{"tid":140342,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次比咗男友 但佢話我唔係處","createTime":"2017-03-02T06:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T18:41:35.000Z","uid":156,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d39d92357fbe7a249989b24d8d25d1d83c00a080","tid":140342,"uid":156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"我27歲，同男友拍咗大約3年拖，佢係我第一個，佢32歲。<br />\n<br />\n我希望隻豬係留比自己最愛嘅男人，最好係老公。拍拖3年，我知道佢一直想要，但我都冇比 拒絕咗。到最近開始談婚論嫁，一個月前佢向我求婚，一次興起，我地發生咗關係。就係咁，我處女之身比左佢。<br />\n<br />\n完事之後，冇流血冇性，床都冇，佢個樣好失望，之後我一直覺得佢介意，覺得我唔係處。<br />\n直至尋日，我唔多舒服，佢想要，我話唔好<br />\n<br />\n佢講咗一句，其實你扮乜野，根本一直唔係處啦！<br />\n<br />\n我聽到好激動不停喊，我一直想留最好嘅嘢比佢，但竟然喺佢口中聽到d咁樣嘅說話！佢今日不停whatsapp我話知道自己錯，但原來佢係咁睇我，有冇流血係咁重要嗎？各位sis認為我仲應該同佢結婚定要重新考慮！求大家比意見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9c659a258229d4c35bfa65f87af52efb2d5beb","tid":140342,"uid":4494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">This</span></span>"},{"pid":"513177cacc971394701960d47f6ca8a1bcbe2057","tid":140342,"uid":5918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">This</span></span>"},{"pid":"491560d5651303446e2b9a113c376e356d061886","tid":140342,"uid":8306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"係你瀨屎先俾人發現你非處"},{"pid":"9c4f6460a503aa8caa3aa306ac2bdab4b786c1d4","tid":140342,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"你抄文都要貼 source 啦"},{"pid":"4c7caf1c2d26d0e7e2482117c0cfb1cae6f203ed","tid":140342,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T06:21:08.000Z","msg":"括約肌有彈性唔係錯"},{"pid":"b1f671ed9585e96c918d753899ed4f298e2c2c68","tid":140342,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc